1
00:00:13,240 --> 00:00:15,119
You bitch, you're asking for it!

2
00:00:23,559 --> 00:00:25,039
Harassing me in public!

3
00:00:25,039 --> 00:00:26,079
You must have a death wish!

4
00:00:26,440 --> 00:00:26,719
Get lost!

5
00:00:27,760 --> 00:00:28,559
You just wait!

6
00:00:30,359 --> 00:00:30,960
Just you wait!

7
00:00:55,679 --> 00:00:56,479
Are you okay?

8
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:24,040
Grandfather.

9
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:27,079
Are you really working with Ren Feifan?

10
00:01:28,319 --> 00:01:28,879
What's the matter?

11
00:01:30,719 --> 00:01:31,359
Nothing.

12
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:34,799
I just don't think he can be trusted.

13
00:01:35,959 --> 00:01:36,799
Why not?

14
00:01:37,799 --> 00:01:39,599
It's all clearly written in black and white.

15
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:40,959
He holds the operating rights.

16
00:01:41,719 --> 00:01:45,159
For this kid to bounce back so quickly,

17
00:01:45,719 --> 00:01:46,319
I'm certain

18
00:01:47,599 --> 00:01:48,879
someone powerful is backing him.

19
00:01:50,239 --> 00:01:52,280
But we only supply medicinal herbs.

20
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:54,000
We're upstream suppliers for the drugs.

21
00:01:54,359 --> 00:01:56,319
When it comes to operations,

22
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:59,439
the Wang family still runs Northern City.

23
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:01,400
The Wang family?

24
00:02:02,719 --> 00:02:03,920
Truly a woman's shortsightedness.

25
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:06,799
You think I'm after the forty percent

26
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:08,319
of Northern City's market he holds?

27
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:12,280
Do you know what the Wanli Pill really is?

28
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:15,960
After its southern launch two years ago,

29
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,520
it dominated the entire market.

30
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:20,159
Forty percent is just the beginning.

31
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:23,680
I will seize the entire northern market.

32
00:02:25,039 --> 00:02:26,280
Through Ren Feifan,

33
00:02:27,599 --> 00:02:29,280
I'll meet the man behind him.

34
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:32,080
Once I take over the Wanli Pill market,

35
00:02:33,039 --> 00:02:33,800
by that time,

36
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:35,759
the Wang family

37
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:37,479
won't be worth a damn.

38
00:02:38,639 --> 00:02:39,680
But Grandfather,

39
00:02:40,319 --> 00:02:41,719
I don't think our family

40
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:44,919
ever had an exclusive government project.

41
00:02:46,919 --> 00:02:47,639
Exactly.

42
00:02:48,439 --> 00:02:50,120
You and your second uncle get on it now.

43
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:52,680
Find a new project within a month.

44
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:16,719
Why did you drink so much?

45
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:18,719
Bartender.

46
00:03:19,639 --> 00:03:20,400
A whiskey, please.

47
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:20,759
Thanks.

48
00:03:20,759 --> 00:03:21,039
Never mind.

49
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:22,639
Give her a glass of water.

50
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:26,919
Feifan, I'm really not drunk.

51
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:28,840
I can hold my liquor.

52
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:30,039
You know that.

53
00:03:32,719 --> 00:03:33,680
What about my grandfather?

54
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:35,199
He's already started preparing.

55
00:03:36,319 --> 00:03:37,479
That man

56
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:40,919
is arrogant and conceited.

57
00:03:42,159 --> 00:03:44,800
Worst of all, he's eager for success.

58
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:48,159
Wang Chengren has crushed him for years.

59
00:03:48,599 --> 00:03:49,960
And he really resents it.

60
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:53,039
Don't worry.

61
00:03:53,599 --> 00:03:54,599
He'll definitely take the bait.

62
00:03:55,319 --> 00:04:00,680
After all, you dangled such a huge carrot.

63
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:03,360
Sober up.

64
00:04:06,159 --> 00:04:06,479
Sit.

65
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,159
Don't worry.

66
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:12,800
It's not just an empty promise.

67
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:14,639
All of it is real.

68
00:04:15,479 --> 00:04:17,839
It's just that the contracts and projects

69
00:04:18,519 --> 00:04:19,720
aren't for Li Qiankun.

70
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:21,120
They're for you.

71
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:24,360
As my thanks for helping me.

72
00:04:28,319 --> 00:04:29,319
Ren Feifan.

73
00:04:33,639 --> 00:04:34,759
You know,

74
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:36,879
you're perfect in every way.

75
00:04:39,079 --> 00:04:40,360
The only flaw

76
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,759
is that you just don't love me.

77
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:56,279
But it doesn't matter.

78
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:58,879
If you don't love me,

79
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,360
Then I'll focus on my career.

80
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:06,319
All I need is a lot of money.

81
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:10,920
Shen Yue.

82
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:13,079
You're truly wonderful.

83
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:14,800
Someday

84
00:05:15,839 --> 00:05:17,120
you'll find someone who truly loves you.

85
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:12,240
Ruojin.

86
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,560
In this city,

87
00:06:30,199 --> 00:06:31,879
people die every single night.

88
00:06:33,199 --> 00:06:34,519
A lot of people die.

89
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:37,120
The truly wicked ones,

90
00:06:37,319 --> 00:06:38,480
the innocent ones,

91
00:06:40,519 --> 00:06:41,360
and also

92
00:06:42,439 --> 00:06:44,759
those obsessed with revenge.

93
00:06:50,839 --> 00:06:51,800
Revenge...

94
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,079
Don't.

95
00:06:56,279 --> 00:06:57,120
Don't, Feifan.

96
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,399
Don't seek revenge.

97
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,120
Revenge is so dangerous.

98
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:04,000
I don't want a repeat of four years ago.

99
00:07:04,959 --> 00:07:05,399
Don't.

100
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,319
Feifan, don't.

101
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,360
Don't repeat

102
00:07:15,319 --> 00:07:16,639
what happened four years ago...

103
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,160
That deadly trap.

104
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:21,639
You're not Xu Ruojin.

105
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:23,279
Get away from me.

106
00:07:31,399 --> 00:07:32,120
Feifan.

107
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,079
It's me.

108
00:07:34,519 --> 00:07:35,360
I'm Ruojin.

109
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:39,360
Please, love me one more time.

110
00:07:40,279 --> 00:07:40,879
Feifan.

111
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:22,039
Feifan.

112
00:09:22,919 --> 00:09:23,600
Let it go.

113
00:09:24,279 --> 00:09:25,039
Don't seek revenge.

114
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:27,480
Leave this place.

115
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:38,480
Last night was pretty relaxing, wasn't it?

116
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:41,600
It's really good for your condition.

117
00:09:42,519 --> 00:09:43,759
I wasn't there for treatment.

118
00:09:45,039 --> 00:09:46,799
But he really is a doctor.

119
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:48,360
Loves sticking needles in his patients.

120
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:50,240
Needles are great.

121
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,200
Isn't he the root of your illness?

122
00:09:54,159 --> 00:09:57,200
Last week you said the window was crying.

123
00:09:57,639 --> 00:09:58,720
So, what about now?

124
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:03,000
It's not just the window anymore.

125
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:06,720
The day before yesterday... that morning.

126
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:09,240
I... I heard the kitchen coffee machine...

127
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:11,759
in Feifan's voice, calling me despicable.

128
00:10:11,879 --> 00:10:13,639
This is all a setup.

129
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:16,120
I won't spare a single one of them.

130
00:10:16,399 --> 00:10:17,080
It's my fault.

131
00:10:17,399 --> 00:10:18,279
Don't arrest him!

132
00:10:18,279 --> 00:10:18,919
Don't take him away!

133
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:20,240
You called the police?

134
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,279
If it weren't for me...

135
00:10:21,919 --> 00:10:24,120
Without me, Feifan wouldn't be in prison.

136
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:26,279
Am I... am I losing my mind?

137
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:29,120
Ruojin, do you remember?

138
00:10:29,639 --> 00:10:32,639
In college, I broke down over my thesis.

139
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:36,120
You told me I could just pick a new topic.

140
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:38,360
Any mistake can be fixed.

141
00:10:41,639 --> 00:10:42,480
Fixed.

142
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,480
Four years ago, I called the police.

143
00:10:45,399 --> 00:10:46,279
Wang Wenhao and his crew...

144
00:10:46,279 --> 00:10:48,360
tore Feifan's family apart like vultures.

145
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:49,799
And now...

146
00:10:51,639 --> 00:10:52,200
Now...

147
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:54,720
they're back again.

148
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:57,440
They... they're back again.

149
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:58,960
Ruojin, calm down.

150
00:10:59,159 --> 00:11:00,399
Just calm down.

151
00:11:01,159 --> 00:11:02,159
Ruojin.

152
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:04,399
Ning Le.

153
00:11:04,879 --> 00:11:06,639
Avenging the Ren family should be my job.

154
00:11:07,039 --> 00:11:07,480
But...

155
00:11:09,039 --> 00:11:10,399
But I'm so useless.

156
00:11:11,399 --> 00:11:13,320
My wedding to Wang Wenhao is almost here.

157
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:15,440
And I still haven't found anything.

158
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:17,519
I haven't found a thing.

159
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,399
Feifan is out. How can I help him?

160
00:11:19,399 --> 00:11:21,080
It's okay, it's okay.

161
00:11:22,399 --> 00:11:23,320
Let's not think about it for now.

162
00:11:25,919 --> 00:11:26,679
What do I do?

163
00:11:27,399 --> 00:11:29,200
Congratulations, congratulations!

164
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:32,759
Best of luck on the opening!

165
00:11:32,759 --> 00:11:34,159
Good luck, good luck!

166
00:11:34,159 --> 00:11:35,039
Congrats on the opening!

167
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:37,759
It's really open now.

168
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:39,000
Greet the guests first, greet the guests.

169
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,080
Please, please, come in!

170
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,440
Come in, come in.

171
00:11:43,639 --> 00:11:44,440
Congratulations!

172
00:11:48,159 --> 00:11:48,759
Let's go, let's go.

173
00:11:48,879 --> 00:11:49,360
Go on.

174
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:52,320
Look over here.

175
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:53,279
The decor looks great too.

176
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:54,279
Congratulations!

177
00:11:54,399 --> 00:11:55,639
Thanks.

178
00:11:55,759 --> 00:11:56,759
Make way, make way!

179
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:57,720
Congratulations!

180
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:59,720
Please, hurry, save Old Qian!

181
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:01,320
Dr. Ren, please save Old Qian!

182
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:02,080
He's really not going to make it.

183
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:03,159
What are you doing here?

184
00:12:03,840 --> 00:12:04,759
What am I doing here?

185
00:12:04,759 --> 00:12:06,120
I'm here to heal the sick and save lives.

186
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:23,919
He's been poisoned.

187
00:12:24,039 --> 00:12:25,279
Take him in and pump his stomach first.

188
00:12:26,559 --> 00:12:28,679
Doctor, isn't today your grand opening?

189
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:30,679
I've set up a livestream here.

190
00:12:31,279 --> 00:12:32,279
Just treat him right here.

191
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:33,759
Xiaohu.

192
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:36,720
Stop streaming to gain popularity.

193
00:12:37,399 --> 00:12:38,679
Bring the phone closer.

194
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:40,360
Get a good shot.

195
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,879
Of how Doctor Ren saves lives.

196
00:12:42,759 --> 00:12:43,759
How many times have I told you?

197
00:12:47,120 --> 00:12:47,840
So, Doctor Ren?

198
00:12:48,919 --> 00:12:49,799
Have you figured it out?

199
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:55,440
Looks like Doctor Ren can't figure it out.

200
00:12:59,399 --> 00:13:00,320
This Premier Medical Hall...

201
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:02,039
has centuries of history,

202
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:04,320
passed down through generations.

203
00:13:04,919 --> 00:13:06,799
Even Premier Medical Hall can't cure this.

204
00:13:08,039 --> 00:13:09,000
Maybe this signboard...

205
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:10,840
should just come down.

206
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:14,240
It's Gut-Breaking Grass.

207
00:13:19,919 --> 00:13:20,840
Then what about Gut-Breaking Grass?

208
00:13:21,879 --> 00:13:22,679
How do you cure it?

209
00:13:23,399 --> 00:13:25,080
Gut-Breaking Grass has no antidote.

210
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:33,320
Everyone heard that, right?

211
00:13:34,399 --> 00:13:37,480
Premier Medical Hall says Gut-Breaking Grass has no cure.

212
00:13:38,519 --> 00:13:39,720
But as far as I know,

213
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:42,279
Gut-Breaking Grass does have an antidote.

214
00:13:43,519 --> 00:13:46,519
Is Premier Medical Hall refusing to help,

215
00:13:47,159 --> 00:13:48,080
or do they truly not know?

216
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:52,679
If they're refusing to save him,

217
00:13:53,759 --> 00:13:56,679
then this signboard should come down.

218
00:13:57,159 --> 00:13:58,399
If they genuinely don't know,

219
00:13:58,799 --> 00:14:00,039
then their skills are lacking.

220
00:14:00,559 --> 00:14:02,039
Running a clinic in Northern City,

221
00:14:02,679 --> 00:14:05,320
you wouldn't feel safe being treated here.

222
00:14:05,480 --> 00:14:06,039
Exactly.

223
00:14:06,159 --> 00:14:08,360
'Decades of family tradition' is a scam.

224
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:10,840
I hear many clinics these days are frauds.

225
00:14:10,919 --> 00:14:12,440
There is one cure for Gut-Breaking Grass.
